</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>1 (RL+) - 2 (RL-)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>Below 2.2 kΩ</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>1 (RL+) - Body ground</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>10 kΩ or higher</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>2 (RL-) - Body ground</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>10 kΩ or higher</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</spec>
<ptxt>If the value is not as specified, replace the skid control sensor.</ptxt>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
